{"tid":842020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生不馨香 蔡瀾食店最高月薪1.8萬請侍應","createTime":"2018-09-30T03:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T14:22:45.000Z","uid":121464,"like":29,"dislike":218,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"11bf93a236f237ab21905b9911def441166afdc5","tid":842020,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"全職員工工作10小時　試用期15000元月薪<br />\n<br />\n該店舖人員稱，全職員工一般每日需工作<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">約10小時</span></span>，工作分早晚兩更。首三個月的試用期間底薪為約15,000元，另在勤工獎、交通津貼下，料薪金可再多1,000元。假期方面則為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6天工作制，每月有4天假期</span></span>，有公眾假期可再補放。他更表示，試用期完結後會再加人工。<br />\n<br />\n在介紹完職責及福利後，店舖人員隨即向記者查詢是否有意應徵，簡單了解曾否有餐廳工作經驗、如「捱唔捱得苦」後，便同意可按記者的情況盡快到店舖試工。<br />\n<br />\n咁都好吹奏 18000買得起你成個人 你都幾cheap<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/235099/大學生不馨香-飲食業高薪求才-蔡瀾食店最高月薪1-8萬請侍應\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F235099%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E9%A6%A8%E9%A6%99-%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E6%A5%AD%E9%AB%98%E8%96%AA%E6%B1%82%E6%89%8D-%E8%94%A1%E7%80%BE%E9%A3%9F%E5%BA%97%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA1-8%E8%90%AC%E8%AB%8B%E4%BE%8D%E6%87%89&d=VgDisFYbR%2F7l5trZ3dsCHG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=27b37a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/235099/大學生不馨香-飲食業高薪求才-蔡瀾食店最高月薪1-8萬請侍應</a>"},{"pid":"3c2156055f15b48e31723ad9d4687b5f8bae859f","tid":842020,"uid":132587,"like":438,"dislike":5,"score":433,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"寧願做條三文魚都唔會做呢d垃圾工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5733c48c0a4180a0c25a80e733a21252401d46b1","tid":842020,"uid":69213,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55fe444918658edf43247de62108e5df1f4f5b8a","tid":842020,"uid":35388,"like":238,"dislike":7,"score":231,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-